Sr. QA\QC Technician job
in Singapore
Job Ref:
15278BR
COUNTRY:
Singapore
CITY:
Singapore
EMPLOYER:
INDUSTRY:
Manufacturing/Production
We are hiring for a QA/ QC Technician role that offers the right individual an opportunity to make a positive difference in the world today. You will join a vibrant and team oriented department with an opportunity to develop and grow a career within a truly global company. Why Thermo Fisher Scientific? We are a $17 billion company with over 50,000 employees worldwide and we look after our staff. On top of attractive bonus payouts, industry standard overtime payments and a unique 'no shift work' practice, we have a variety of staff benefits that will cover you and your immediate family. If you are looking to be part of an organization that champions progress and growth while making the world a healthier, cleaner and safer place, look no further. Responsibilities
Perform hands-on failure investigations of returned products from customers to find the root cause of failure Document investigation findings in failure analysis report Support FA Engineer to ensure fast turn-around of instrument failure analysis Handle returned, used devices in compliance with company policies Supports company goals and objectives, policies and procedures in compliance with quality systems, cGMP and FDA regulationsMinimum Qualifications (must have)
Able to work independently
Ability to communicate concisely on technical issues
Minimum 3 years of relevant experience / NTC 3 in Engineering
Must possess a strong desire for hands-on work in a lab environment
Proficient in MS Office
*LI-NG1 Preferred Qualifications (nice to have)NAEOE
Post Date:
05/03/2014
